{"tid":2011174,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【一矢中的】泛民，與WHO力架毫無分別！","createTime":"2020-05-10T22:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T10:00:35.000Z","uid":202464,"like":21,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c1331f076936b108a51e9583751e70b4ec7e4b","tid":2011174,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T22:33:57.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉又到，含淚投票的口號又浮上水面。大敵當前，「同心合力不分化」說起來相當順口，令人想起世衛主腦譚德塞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n◉ 名為反對派的共犯<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞：<br />\n把中共的說詞照單全收，抗疫方針亦是用中共的準則判斷，又對中共讚美和辯護。當疫情變得嚴重，才慢條斯理的說情況已經有變，彷彿一切都是意料之外。<br />\n<br />\n泛民：<br />\n相當信任中共的承諾，例如「五十年不變」、「港人高度自治」，到後來的「高鐵不會超支」之類，都是在提出之際不反抗，後來才一副「點解會咁架」的驚恐樣子。<br />\n面對騙徒慣犯還多番中招，這個到底是「受害者」還是「共犯」，就自然不言而喻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n◉ 情緒勒索三十載<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞：<br />\n在疫情仍然嚴峻的時候，世界各國應合作，不應該互相指責，才可以同心抗疫。同時，世衛作為「全球抗疫指揮總部」的地位，令其佔據道德高地，支持世衛就是支持抗疫，批評世衛就是與人類作對。如此的權威聲音，令一眾名人歌手、國際企業、社交平台紛紛臣服。<br />\n<br />\n泛民：<br />\n光是從「泛民主派」這個稱號，就知道它已經與民主運動劃上等號。就像世衛一樣，泛民自從八十年代就已經是民主「大台」，每當有選舉，看到泛民蓋下去就是。權威嘛，得服從。反對泛民，就是反對民主運動，就是破壞之前所作的努力成果。<br />\n<br />\n可惜的是，抗共在泛民的指揮底下永遠不會看到盡頭，只會是 Tom and Jerry 式的打情罵俏，消費民怨至淨盡。"},{"pid":"e4dbd7fdd811eb02c9e42ea551402397397f7728","tid":2011174,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T22:35:27.000Z","msg":"有一個飯民打手負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216df286aee09ac422801f40dcd7f6c5be6936de","tid":2011174,"uid":125502,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T22:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"ba7efb4f59487874f4da039c2f83db151c949508","tid":2011174,"uid":60164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T22:39:10.000Z","msg":"汽車推推"},{"pid":"681309c5bce9e523a4a14d401267021d1c91d341","tid":2011174,"uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T23:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.if\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.if&h=8900928b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n左膠：「用愛與和平，穿透坦克」"},{"pid":"a4095459e9c3d705f66985e7e6ddca209ca7f9dd","tid":2011174,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"飯民打手永遠都唔敢入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一次證明樓主擊中要害！"},{"pid":"bfecc520ea15fcdfec1d4f5d7126343575a678fd","tid":2011174,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T23:46:13.000Z","msg":"有請飯民打手入黎講幾句<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93152b481719694394c7a574bfc1a5406c45b34","tid":2011174,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T23:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJQTxtT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJQTxtT.gif&h=6ab11bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/11/075830_70202c2ece7a7e6e7991bd3cf537795a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F1